'''Palar''' was an influential computer manufacturer on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]. They worked almost exclusively for [[Imperial Intelligence/Legends|Imperial Intelligence]] and had several facilities in the [[Alien Protection Zone/Legends|Invisible Sector]] of [[Galactic City/Legends|Imperial City]]. Their main production included the manufacture of essential [[Memory bank/Legends|memory cores]] for use in Imperial computer systems. To maintain a high rate of production, the company was given access to a "disposable" alien force that was constantly being replaced. Thus huge quantities of memory cores were produced at almost no cost.

